Name: Add-Printer
Synopsis: Adds a printer to the specified computer.

Name: Add-PrinterDriver
Synopsis: Installs a printer driver on the specified computer.

Name: Add-PrinterPort
Synopsis: Installs a printer port on the specified computer.

Name: Get-PrintConfiguration
Synopsis: Gets the configuration information of a printer.

Name: Get-Printer
Synopsis: Retrieves a list of printers installed on a computer.

Name: Get-PrinterDriver
Synopsis: Retrieves the list of printer drivers installed on the specified computer.

Name: Get-PrinterPort
Synopsis: Retrieves a list of printer ports installed on the specified computer.

Name: Get-PrinterProperty
Synopsis: Retrieves printer properties for the specified printer.

Name: Get-PrintJob
Synopsis: Retrieves a list of print jobs in the specified printer.

Name: Read-PrinterNfcTag
Synopsis: Reads information about printers from an NFC tag.

Name: Remove-Printer
Synopsis: Removes a printer from the specified computer.

Name: Remove-PrinterDriver
Synopsis: Deletes printer driver from the specified computer.

Name: Remove-PrinterPort
Synopsis: Removes the specified printer port from the specified computer.

Name: Remove-PrintJob
Synopsis: Removes a print job on the specified printer.

Name: Rename-Printer
Synopsis: Renames the specified printer.

Name: Restart-PrintJob
Synopsis: Restarts a print job on the specified printer.

Name: Resume-PrintJob
Synopsis: Resumes a suspended print job.

Name: Set-PrintConfiguration
Synopsis: Sets the configuration information for the specified printer.

Name: Set-Printer
Synopsis: Updates the configuration of an existing printer.

Name: Set-PrinterProperty
Synopsis: Modifies the printer properties for the specified printer.

Name: Suspend-PrintJob
Synopsis: Suspends a print job on the specified printer.

Name: Write-PrinterNfcTag
Synopsis: Writes printer connection data to an NFC tag.
